## Attribution

The design patterns and principles in this plugin are inspired by:

- **5 Agent Skill Design Patterns Every ADK Developer Should Know**
  - Source: [lavinigam.com/posts/adk-skill-design-patterns](https://lavinigam.com/posts/adk-skill-design-patterns/)
  - Author: Lavi Nigam
  - Published: March 7, 2026

- **SoK: Agentic Skills, Beyond Tool Use in LLM Agents**
  - Source: [arxiv.org/html/2602.20867v1](https://arxiv.org/html/2602.20867v1)
  - Authors: Zicheng Huang, Yaxin Liu, Zhengliang Shi, Yuting Jiang, Lu Chen, Kai Yu
  - Published: February 28, 2026

This plugin extracts universal skill design patterns, principles, and benchmark-backed guidance from the original sources, removing framework-specific content. Changes include restructuring, generalization, and adaptation for distribution as a GitHub Copilot CLI plugin.
